  AUTHORS   Li Y, Llewellyn NM, Giri R, Huang F, Spencer JB
  TITLE     Biosynthesis of the unique amino acid side chain of butirosin: possible protective-group chemistry in an acyl carrier protein-mediated pathway.
  JOURNAL   Chem. Biol. 12 (2005) 665-75.
  ORGANISM  Bacillus circulans
  SEQUENCE  [up:Q4H4E7]
PATHWAY     ec00524  Butirosin and neomycin biosynthesis
            ec01110  Biosynthesis of secondary metabolites
